=基础系统(光盘安装)=[base-iso]
- 到http://www.archlinux.org下iso，刻盘。
- 参考：[个人的Arch Linux 安装笔记和步骤简述 http://www.linuxsir.org/bbs/thread317982.html]


==设置arch源==[source]
- 编辑/etc/pacman.conf
```
[archlinuxfr]
Server = http://repo.archlinux.fr/$arch
```
- 编辑/etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist
```
Server = http://mirrors.163.com/archlinux/$repo/os/$arch
```


=基础系统(U盘安装)=[base-usb]
- 下载archlinux最新光盘：http://www.archlinux.org/download/
- 下载LinuxLive USB Creator：http://www.linuxliveusb.com/
- 用LinuxLive USB Creator制作可启动的USB盘
- 修改BIOS，从USB启动，进入archlinux


==硬盘分区==[fdisk]
- 假设系统硬盘为/dev/sda，这边是SSD
- 执行fdisk /dev/sda进行分区，假设新建的系统分区为/dev/sda1
- mkfs -t ext4 -b 4096 -E stride=128,stripe-width=128 /dev/sda1


==安装系统==[intall-init]
- 执行wifi-menu，连接合适的无线网络
- 编辑/etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist，选择合适的server，比如163.com的源就比较快
```
mount /dev/sda1 /mnt
pacstrap /mnt base base-devel
pacstrap /mnt grub2-bios
genfstab -p /mnt >> /mnt/etc/fstab
arch-chroot /mnt
```
- 设置arch源，见上节
```
ln -s /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime
mkinitcpio -p linux
grub-install --no-floppy /dev/sda
grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg
pacman -S net-tools wireless_tools wpa_supplicant netcfg ifplugd dialog
exit
reboot
```
- 重启之后，执行wifi-menu连接到无线网络


