=热插拔=[hotplug]
- yaourt -S ntfs-3g mount-tray
- 配置 /etc/fstab
```
/dev/sdb1 /mnt/usb ntfs-3g auto,users,permissions 0 0
```
- 设置mount-tray随X启动即可


=网络=[network]
==根据MAC地址固定网卡名称==[card]
编辑文件/etc/udev/rules.d/10-network.rules
```
SUBSYSTEM=="net", ATTR{address}=="00:26:2d:f6:ad:43", NAME="eth0"
SUBSYSTEM=="net", ATTR{address}=="70:f1:a1:28:5a:ad", NAME="wlan0"
```


==无线(NetworkManager)==[wireless-networkmanager]
- 安装: yaourt -S networkmanager xfce4-notifyd network-manager-applet nm-applet 
- 配置: 进入xfce4后，有图形界面配置
- 开机启动：编辑/etc/rc.conf
